node.title: Police continue hunt for missing Otago man
node.description: Police searching for a missing Central Otago man have been re-enacting his last known movements this morning.
node.content:
["Police searching for a missing Central Otago man have been re-enacting his last known movements this morning.", "", "
Missing man Wayne Hammond Photo: NZ Police
", "Wayne Hammond, 50, was last seen leaving his Henderson Drive home in Alexandra in his work car at 7.30am on 1 November.", "His 1999 white-silver Mitsubishi Challenger 4WD was found in the car park underneath the Clyde Bridge at the start of the Clyde-Alexandra track at about 3pm that day.", "It has 'RockGas' printed on the side.", "The police are asking anyone who may have seen the vehicle last Monday to contact them."]
